<D>__{who said sidney?}
<C>__{susan}
<P>__{(defiantly)}
<D>__{i said sidney!...}
<A>__{staring, he pauses; then he deftly changes the subject.}
<C>__{hunsecker}
<D>__{you know, dear, we're drifting apart, you and i, and i don't like that.}
<C>__{susan}
<D>__{i thought we were talking about sidney?}
