<C>__{susan}
<P>__{(interrupting)}
<D>__{i haven't said anything yet, j.j., but if }
<A>__{susan hesitates. hunsecker waits for her to continue. but she isn't yet sure enough of herself or of the point she means to make. she turns away.}
<C>__{hunsecker}
<P>__{(gently)}
